thread.title: Catalan ex-leader to face German court amid protests

title: Catalan ex-leader to face German court amid protests
text:
Catalan ex-leader to face German court amid protests Monday, March 26, 2018 - 02:16 
Former Catalan president Carles Puigdemont is due to appear in a German court on Monday as Spain seeks to extradite him over the region's independence fight after a night of protests there in which dozens of people were hurt in clashes with police.
